{"tid":2028260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"方力申戶外健身被愛犬咬屁股︰防狗之心不可無","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:26:06.000Z","uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b01cdc5745b9a8b4c3aa7853869890c7d0415e","tid":2028260,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"方力申（小方）近日接受健身挑戰，要做足30日，且每隔6日才可休息一天，因此小方不時在社交網分享其健身片段。<br />\n<br />\n豈料，他今日在戶外地方做引體上升時遇上意外，被突然衝出來的一頭黑狗咬屁股和腳，小方差點被咬甩褲，露出淺色內褲。非常狼狽的他立即跳落地喝令黑狗，但黑狗仍未罷休，繼續咬住他的手臂不放，結果小方的手臂和腳都受了傷，留下幾道血痕。"},{"pid":"2a080b4bbf6cc1237520c10365998e45e21ffc04","tid":2028260,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200521/s00009/22240ebca22e81c098e91945622ccb9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200521%2Fs00009%2F22240ebca22e81c098e91945622ccb9a.jpg&h=d72476ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5b8504fc31fad541c4109169e68ba6ef8cd6f70","tid":2028260,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"小方留言︰「『內有惡犬』，原來不只是用來警告外面的人，連裡（裏）面的人也要注意！特別是主人，因為他應該是最沒有防備心的！#中招 #三喜 #連老細都咬 #損咗少少 #防狗之心不可無」吳若希留言︰「🤣🤣🤣我屋企隻Honey都係咁ga（㗎）～ 佢驚你有危險～ 咬返（番）你落嚟～～」"},{"pid":"bebbff620965ff1f906b90865714e9def6d3a789","tid":2028260,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"點解佢游水咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49710417f76775a4951f3fd552e8e641fd071bb5","tid":2028260,"uid":24457,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"#防狗之心不可無<br />\n都講到好出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4bb6e2488ef7f3ab6ed96230fc3d119b757acd","tid":2028260,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49710417f76775a4951f3fd552e8e641fd071bb5","tid":2028260,"uid":24457,"like":35,"dislike":1,"